            <h1 itemprop="headline"><a href="/2015/09/28/web-design-standards/">Introducing the U.S. Web Design Standards</a></h1>
          </div>

          <div class="blog-meta">
            <p>
              Posted on
              <time class="blog-date" datetime="2015-09-28T00:00:00+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">
                28 Sep 2015
              </time>
            </p>
            <p>
              Tagged /
              <span class="blog-tags" itemprop="keywords">
                
                  <a href="/tags/proactive%20federal%20partner">proactive federal partner</a>
                  /
                
                  <a href="/tags/our%20projects">our projects</a>
